game_headlines.headline: J&K Electric crushes Colson Overhead Doors 6-3 powered by Brendan Stone's hat trick, while Jeremy Kinnear supplying brace (2G)
G.R. Mitchell Welding trounces Ultramar 9-3 sparked by Dave Atkinson's brace (2G) and 1A, while Meathead MacDonald supplying 1G and 3A
J&K Electric squeaks by Maltby Sports 4-3 lifted by Rubein Mackenzie's brace (2G), as Avery Harrison chipping in 1G and 1A
G.R. Mitchell Welding routs Colson Overhead Doors 12-3 fueled by Meathead MacDonald's hat trick and 4A, with Ryan Macpherson contributing brace (2G)
Maltby Sports steamrolls Ultramar 9-5 sparked by Madden Miller's brace (2G), with Tyler "Tuffy" Allen adding brace (2G)
G.R. Mitchell Welding cruises past J&K Electric 5-2 fueled by Meathead MacDonald's 1G and 2A, and Gordon Mitchell supplying 1G and 1A
Maltby Sports routs G.R. Mitchell Welding 10-2 fueled by Thomas Mccrossin's hat trick and 1A, with Danny "Biggie" Small supplying brace (2G) and 3A
J&K Electric pummels Colson Overhead Doors 6-1 lifted by Rubein Mackenzie's brace (2G) and 1A, as Pat Morris chipping in 1G and 3A
Maltby Sports cruises past Ultramar 7-4 sparked by Issac Bridge's hat trick (4G) and 1A, and Ian McCarthy supplying 1G and 3A
